name: THESINS//003 : BEGINNING
description:
ACT//003. BREAKFAST SCENE.

May remember everything like it was yesterday. Nine in the morning, coffee in her hand, trembled. Sat in front of her, was Carl, man she’s been married for 5 years, upset. 
‘Don't you think I don't know?’ Asked Carl. 
'I’m not happy.’ She said.
Carl looked at May, and the saddest thing was he’s no longer surprised when she broke his heart.
